Acquisition:
   - Assassin: level 48
Description:
   Cloak:transcendence is the Assassin's signature remort cloak. It envelops
   the caster in a shimmering aura of transcendent agility, granting a small
   chance to completely avoid incoming physical attacks.

   When the caster would take physical damage, there is a pseudo_level / 15
   percent chance that the Assassin transcends the strike entirely, taking no
   damage. For example, at pseudo-level 150, there is a 10% chance to avoid
   each physical hit.

   The cloak does not protect against non-physical (spell) damage. For
   magical avoidance, see cloak:oathbreaker (Warlock).

   Duration scales with pseudo-level (pseudo_level / 8 rounds).
*******************************************************************************
